title: Bug 121682 Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Add a table that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 
2. Preview the attached report. 
3. Export the data from the table.
